#: ../../docs/classes/class_visualshadernodecubemap.rst:43
msgid ""
"**SOURCE_TEXTURE** = **0** --- Use the :ref:`Cubemap <class_Cubemap>` set"
" via :ref:`cube_map <class_VisualShaderNodeCubemap_property_cube_map>`. "
"If this is set to :ref:`source "
"<class_VisualShaderNodeCubemap_property_source>`, the ``samplerCube`` "
"port is ignored."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_visualshadernodecubemap.rst:45
msgid ""
"**SOURCE_PORT** = **1** --- Use the :ref:`Cubemap <class_Cubemap>` "
"sampler reference passed via the ``samplerCube`` port. If this is set to "
":ref:`source <class_VisualShaderNodeCubemap_property_source>`, the "
":ref:`cube_map <class_VisualShaderNodeCubemap_property_cube_map>` texture"
" is ignored."
msgstr ""

